{
  "stem": "7592.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And once in a while, we got some additional food from the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They gave us tobacco.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you couldn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll give you an example.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The  Red Cross came in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were in preparation-- maybe you saw the movie-- Theresienstadt, how they prepared some Red Cross or some came.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were instructions.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If we asked questions-- an example, Goeth used to stay behind the commission, and ask, how many breads are you getting?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Goeth, behind us, showed two fingers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Naturally, if you didn't say what he showed you, you'll be dead in a half hour after the commission leave.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this was the--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometime we got cheeses of some kind from-- from the Red Cross-- powdered milk or something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it helped, but it wasn't every day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and Schindler, the same thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like I said, Schindler, I wouldn't say, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] like he-- he was-- I wouldn't take away from him what he did, but why  he did-- to save himself, he needed people over there in Brunnlitz so they can testify.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He put some shows over there so he could remember what he did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After the war, naturally, Schindler was supported by us-- contribution, money, incentives.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They gave him $30,000 right away from the-- from the Joint.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a drunkard, a womanizer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He put it-- and in a few months, there was nothing left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then they collected money again for him so he could go to Argentina.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they brought him over there-- I don't know-- the same thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1942, when he figured out how I got so much money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got so many jewelry-- how to keep this, and stay-- because he'd be a millionaire after the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
